PhD (Statistics), The University of Newcastle, Aust.
Dr Howley is a 2015 National Award Winner (Office for Learning and Teaching Citation) and The University of Newcastle’s 2014 Vice-Chancellor’s Award Winner for Teaching Excellence and Contribution to Student Learning.
